# GLPX Default CODEOWNERS
# This file is used by both GitHub and Gitea to automatically request reviews
# from the appropriate team members when specific files are modified in a Pull Request.
#
# As this is located in the organizational template repository, it acts as a fallback
# for any repository in the organization that does not define its own CODEOWNERS file.

# Global fallback: By default, ask the main maintainer (Damir) for review
* @mukimovd

# Require DevOps/Infrastructure review for critical core files
/.github/ @mukimovd
/.gitea/ @mukimovd
/Makefile @mukimovd
Dockerfile @mukimovd

# Infrastructure as Code (Helm/Kustomize)
/charts/ @mukimovd
/manifests/ @mukimovd
/helm/ @mukimovd
/kustomize/ @mukimovd

# CI/CD Pipelines (Gitea Actions only; .github/ holds community files, no workflows)
/.gitea/workflows/ @mukimovd
